  "title": "1.3 roadmap",
  "body": "This is a living roadmap of the 1.3 release, please comment\n## Features\n- [x] implement a query hook #817\n  ~~\\- [ ] add `hasChildren` template data to the hierarchical item template #818~~ canceled, need more work\n- [x] menu widget should implement showMore #815 (released as 1.2.2, should have been in 1.2.0)\n## Bugs\n- [x] searchBox value should be updated when query updated programatically from the helper #729 \n- [ ] searchBox should be cleared when reset button present and pressed #804 \n- [x] base attribute not playing well with url sync #790\n## Tests\n- [ ] full functional test suite #814\n- [ ] unit test url sync #243 \n- [ ] unit test menu #237 \n## Docs\n- [x] precise default theme specifics #819\n- [x] md5 documentation assets to avoid caching issues #816 \n",
